## gf 

 - works great with route.rb "user#index"
 - works great in controllers as well, you do not need Rview, Rmodel here! 

## ack

sudo apt-get install ack-grep
sudo ln -s /usr/bin/ack-grep /usr/bin/ack

then in vim

    :Ack xxx

or maybe have this in .vimrc

    map ,k :Ack <cword><ENTER>
